    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "前よりも体力ついたんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "has your stamina got better compared to before?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3656204535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_04_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-05.m4a",
      "text": "昔なら、同じくらい走ったらしばらく動けなく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the past‚ if you ran like that‚ you'd be unable to move for a while‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.266666333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_04_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "なってたでしょ？　ぜひーぜひーって息切れしちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You'd be panting like crazy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1298760833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.933334144
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
