      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そういえば最近よくランニングに付き合ってくれるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ you've been accompanying me on my runs a lot lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1666674774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_04_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-11.m4a",
      "text": "それに気付いたら仕事以外でもずっと勉強してるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I've noticed you've been studying a lot even outside of work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5178239506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
