      "text": "表に出る気はないよ。ただ、麻奈の仕事をほどほどに\nセーブするのは現実的じゃないって分かったからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't have any intention of appearing on TV.\nI just realized that it's not realistic to make you work less.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
